1. *Kuće* su se nalazile u starom gradu. (The houses were located in the old town.)
2. Svi su svoje *kuće* videli u sjajnom svetlu. (Everyone saw their houses in a brilliant light.) 
3. Deca su trčala ispred *kuća*. (The children were running in front of the houses.)
4. Oni su se vratili u svoje *kuće*. (They returned to their homes.)
5. Ona je živela u svojoj *kući*. (She lived in her house.)
6. On je ljubio svoju *kuću*. (He loved his home.) 
7. *Kuće* su bile uzburkane. (The houses were stirred up.) 
8. Ona je otišla u svoju *kuću*. (She went to her house.)